honest, and straightforward."},{"_createdAt":"2024-11-07T10:12:06Z","_id":"0a00b70c-07db-45d5-888e-052bb4d812c9","_updatedAt":"2026-02-17T08:25:09Z","additionalImages":[{"_key":"f361ab9b0878","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-55f366b1454238c59a3851997479d82d2c7244b3-3118x2042-png","_type":"reference"}}],"awards":null,"body":[{"_key":"3a60b1bbc516","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e138e9637eff0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"pump.science challenges the status quo of scientific discovery by letting participants "},{"_key":"e138e9637eff1","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"speculate on life-extending compounds"},{"_key":"e138e9637eff2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" and craft their own experimental \"longevity cocktails.\" The platform provides live feeds of ongoing experiments, allowing users to monitor the effects of tested compounds on model organisms in real time. Community submissions fuel a continuous feedback loop between curious minds and rigorous biological experimentation."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"categories":[{"_id":"f39b5424-a1ab-481e-bc32-9f9e85e05609","description":null,"title":"Blockchain Integrated Apps"},{"_id":"d06268a9-ce65-47f2-a5e9-501005deb1fa","description":"Decentralized Science","title":"DeSci"},{"_id":"36584ef9-64a8-474c-967a-020f991243fc","description":null,"title":"Smart Contracts"},{"_id":"3abd6ef9-e952-4045-9cca-51b88c40d3db","description":null,"title":"DeFi"}],"challengeLevel":null,"clientAuthor":"Benjels","clientAuthorRole":"CEO","clientImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-127cf982b44f08ebc282ae2fd5727361af7685d9-640x640-jpg","_type":"reference"}},"clientName":"pump.science","clientTestimonial":" Working with the Builderz guys did not feel like working with a dev shop. I had heard horror stories of buidling with an external dev shop and only expected to work with one for a short period of time. The Builderz team has exceeded my expectations in every way, but most of all, that they genuinely feel part of our team. They are pushing us to make the product better as much as we are pushing them. They are just as invested in our success as we are. Their communication is extremely clear, and the processes are tight and efficient. Between all of them, they cover the entire stack for building on Solana, and we wouldn't be where we are without them. If we are successful, it will be because of the incredible attention and care they put in to making our product as strong as it could be. I am so grateful to be working with them, couldn't recommend them any more highly, and would be glad to speak with anyone considering working with them about our top-notch experience","demoVideo":null,"description":"pump.science pioneers an interactive approach to longevity research, merging scientific exploration with a gamified digital experience. Our team at Builderz...","githubLink":"https://github.com/moleculeprotocol","headingOne":"How It Works","headingThree":"In the Press","headingTwo":"Collaboration & Community","isFeatured":true,"keyFeatures":null,"liveSiteLink":"https://pump.science/","mainImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-8e2cdc5fe4138221d876dba2ba7101160a33ce4f-1601x901-png","_type":"reference"}},"mockupImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-d4caa81bf99c031a98d5d8cee9973ccedc122510-1601x901-png","_type":"reference"}},"projectDuration":18,"projectMetrics":"Built for pump.science, this Web3 Application solution handles thousands of daily active users with sub-second transaction finality on Solana.","projectStatus":"in-progress","projectTimeline":null,"projectType":"Web3 Application","publishedAt":"2025-08-10T21:39:53.955Z","relatedProjects":null,"servicesProvided":"$1d","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"pump-science"},"teamMembers":null,"techStack":["Solana","Next.js","TypeScript","Web3.js","TailwindCSS"],"textOne":[{"_key":"bdd9176995af","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"07b1354a53c70","_type":"span","marks":["c0e376796b01"],"text":"pump.science"},{"_key":"a55741442f2f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" offers a step-by-step path for users to participate in real-world longevity research:"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"c0e376796b01","_type":"link","href":"https://pump.science"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e4aa501da4b5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d57ac7d8d68c0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Sign Up & Dive In:"},{"_key":"d57ac7d8d68c1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" New members get instant access to live experiment data streams and can submit their own life-extension hypotheses."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"413b0660f1dc","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"b03abca2f6af0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Speculate, Mix, Compete:"},{"_key":"b03abca2f6af1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" Users forecast, submit, or vote on longevity cocktails-substances believed to impact lifespan."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f6622f5cf8d6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2bc016005e9e0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Track Results in Real Time:"},{"_key":"2bc016005e9e1","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" Transparent dashboards display ongoing and completed experimental outcomes, updated as data comes in from the lab."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a33b67ea51be","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"79f7959a24c30","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Climb the Leaderboards:"},{"_key":"79f7959a24c31","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" Gamified rewards and rankings foster a vibrant, competitive scientific community."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"textThree":[{"_key":"66e5519edfe2","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"591c040601d90","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"pump.science has been featured and discussed by several leading voices in the longevity and biotech space. Highlights include:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7277954bface","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"06196b4acabc0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Profiled in top biohacking and healthspan blogs."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d6abbb51011e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"976905899afc0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Shared and discussed by longevity influencers on social media."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"917c7cae51ca","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"210c35902ff80","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Recognized in community newsletters and podcasts."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"textTwo":[{"_key":"df5595a07902","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"554bb46127290","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"pump.science thrives on a strong open-science ethos. The project fosters:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"de45e1395f5b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1460d76861060","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Open Data Sharing"},{"_key":"1460d76861061","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":": All experiment data are published openly for community review and further analysis."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"870eaa24e6e9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d27a66cc1fe80","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Crowdsourced Science"},{"_key":"d27a66cc1fe81","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":": Anyone, from amateur biohackers to professional researchers, can participate, propose ideas, and drive innovation."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"236ce0e3b547","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0f29c033c0650","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Expert Partnerships"},{"_key":"0f29c033c0651","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":": Collaboration with longevity labs, biotech startups, and research organizations expands the project's reach and credibility."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"theChallenge":[{"_key":"1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1a","_type":"span","text":"pump.science needed a secure, scalable Web3 solution that could handle high traffic while providing a seamless user experience. The challenge was to build on Solana with optimal performance and minimal gas costs."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"theSolution":[{"_key":"52cd4d2bdb91","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"a8d9470bd241","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We delivered a cohesive Web3 platform that revolutionizes longevity research by tokenizing science and real-time transparency. Our tech stack implementation solved pump.science's challenges on multiple levels:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"60f7915ceb8c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"fff15567996f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"cf084ce8ebc3","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d4e710594d75","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Tokenized Research Funding: "},{"_key":"9600ae30e0c8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We built a bonding curve mechanism were each longevity compound receives its own token for example $RIF for Rifampicin, $URO for Urolithin A. As tokens reach market caps of 133 SOL, the fund automatically flow to contract research organizations, CROs, to initiate experiments that start with inexpensive worm studies at just 3 SOL ($500) and then advancing to flies, mice, and eventually human trials as trading fees accumulate. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8099678451c9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"b860dcc3936e","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a37eb09d9ff7","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2073207dfa03","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Real-Time Data Streaming: "},{"_key":"96da1d501bf2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We implemented a complex data pipeline that streams live results directly from labs to platform. Users can watch experiments happening in real-time, see actual lifespan data, movement metrics and survival curves as they're generated, thus transforming scientific research into public science where the community can follow progress. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"dbf31f6c2242","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"56fb7a31bef9","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"ed7107ac28ca","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"686dd8902ea9","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Research To Market:"},{"_key":"f3634d16ec47","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" Latest innovation extends beyond research, pump.science now partners with supplement brands to conduct controlled human studies. Their products represent real-world applications where supplement companies sponsor studies on their compounds, human participants receive the supplements and are tracked for outcomes, efficacy data is generated transparently on-chain, brands gain credible scientific validation that drives trust and token holders can see their research investments translate into actual products. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"50512627a879","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f3da7a289aac","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"cb1a0a68dd53","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0e6b7535c846","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Smart Contract Architecture:"},{"_key":"ee2a6b2f88f6","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" Our smart contract handle complex token economics such as dynamic fee models to prevent bot manipulation, automated liquidity migration to Meteora DEX at set milestones, IP rights management through adhesion contracts that give token holders governance over research outcome. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"2ec3118ad739","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"108d2ffe709d","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"352625943fea","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"71674d4f9dea","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Gamified Prediction Market:"},{"_key":"53efa92b44f6","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" We also created an interface where users can speculate on compounds effects, crowdsourcing buth funding and scientific prediction. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3456d98372af","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"380f99292194","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"35b4a3863906","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"23dc9bca1132","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Public Science Infrastructure:"},{"_key":"e68ba34505a9","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" All data is published on-chain, creating an never before seen level of scientific openness. Basically anyone can analyze the data, make proposals or build on existing research with no gatekeeping. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"9d6354883629","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7d222cba6221","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"ff4e3d583520","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c9e45ed83c05","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Scalable Platform Design:"},{"_key":"33cfccec9d90","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" We built the architecture for expansion beyond the initial compounds, basically supporting unlimited experiments accross different model organisms like worms, flies and mice with extensible data schemas and flexible deployment pipelines."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8a4aa54a73c0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"855231609f70","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"be36c8fab384","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9c3e5f0a4d76","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The result is a platform that has generated more than $1M in volume, creating open access to longevity research while creating funding mechanisms for scientific breakthroughs and drastically reducing research times. pump.science shows that Web3 can accelerate scientific discoveries by bringing together incentives between researchers, funders and the community seeking healthspan innovation. "}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"title":"pump.science - Gamified Longevity Research Platform","valueDelivered":"The pump.science platform has democratized longevity research by opening the gates to citizen scientists worldwide. It delivers:  Real-time transparency: Live data streams build trust and keep users engaged, creating a constant feedback loop between the lab and the community.  Community-powered innovation: Crowdsourced hypotheses and compound submissions accelerate discovery beyond the limits of traditional research pipelines.  Enhanced learning and participation: Gamification transforms complex life sciences into an interactive, educational journey, inspiring more people to learn about and invest in the science of healthspan extension.  By making longevity research collaborative, transparent, and fun, Builderz helped pump.science redefine how the future of aging is investigated and advanced-one experiment, and one user, at a time."},{"_createdAt":"2024-11-07T10:26:13Z","_id":"4b8e25fa-df1e-44db-943c-e74b8a4adc70","_updatedAt":"2026-02-17T08:25:22Z","additionalImages":[{"_key":"c8a80dde56bd","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-9854a4abddad2e788ac818a6ae49e7824bbf6fe9-1184x1952-png","_type":"reference"}}],"awards":null,"body":[{"_key":"auto-4b8e25fa","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"auto-span-4b8e25fa","_type":"span","text":"SEND FOMO is a high-stakes blockchain game on Solana that combines NFT mechanics with game theory. Players compete to mint \"keys\" in a dynamic pricing system..."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"categories":[{"_id":"f39b5424-a1ab-481e-bc32-9f9e85e05609","description":null,"title":"Blockchain Integrated Apps"}],"challengeLevel":null,"clientAuthor":"Irffan","clientAuthorRole":"CEO","clientImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-6d73aa7290b523df